<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Nei lawpna aw ka za'i,
 Lalpa, nei sapna chuh;
 Na thisan lul a kithien di'n,
 Kalvari a luong chun.

[V2]
 Lalpa, ka hung ie,
 Tun ka hun zuon ie!
 Thisan in ei sawpthieng in,
 Kalvari-a luong chun.

[V3]
 2. Hatlo leh gilo in,
 Hung mahleng na hatnan;
 Ka gitlohna Na sawpthieng thei,
 Nin bei keia thiengin.

[V4]
 3. Isu'n ei sam zing hi,
 Gin, hehpih kim nei di'n;
 Kinep, muon ginna kim nei di'n,
 Sietlei leh thangvan ah.

[V5]
 4. Lal Isu'n A pawm hi,
 Nasep thilbawl pha chuh;
 Lungsiet chunga lungsiet beh in,
 Gitloh hatna zo in.

[V6]
 5. Hetchetna chuh A piei,
 Lunggil lunglutte di'n;
 Thiltiem cheng chuh bukim ina,
 Ginna'n ahih phawt chun.

[V7]
 6. Khuhna thisan pak un,
 Lungsiet tatna pak un;
 Pak un, Thilpiek, Lal Krista chuh,
 I Hatnau, Kitupnau!</lyrics>
<title>I HEAR THY WELCOME VOICE</title>
<hymn_number>232</hymn_number>
</song>